			<picture class="hero-picture">
				<source srcset="/images/vinyl-fence-photo.webp" type="image/webp">
				<img src="/images/vinyl-fence-photo.webp" alt="Professional vinyl fence installation in Stockton CA" class="hero-image" loading="eager" width="1200" height="600" />
			</picture>
			<div class="hero-overlay">
				<div class="hero-content">
					<h1>Vinyl Fence Installation in Stockton</h1>
					<p class="hero-subtitle">Maintenance-free vinyl fencing that won't fade, crack, or peel. Available in privacy and picket styles with lifetime durability guarantee.</p>
