						<li>Traditional 3-4 foot picket fence heights</li>
						<li>Classic white picket fence appearance</li>
						<li>Spaced picket or board-on-board styles</li>
						<li>Decorative post caps included</li>
						<li>Curved or straight top rail options</li>
						<li>UV-resistant materials prevent yellowing</li>
						<li>Easy to clean with soap and water</li>
						<li>Perfect for front yard applications</li>
					</ul>
